column4: Hello... I have a bad problem... I have no virus software that can scan all programs and find malware, only fixes registry... and I have a trojan
How can I diagnose this? On htop I get like 12% memory usage overall(on files clickable) and it shows 100% at top
Hello... Can anyone point me towards a virus software that's free and downloadable?
and that I can scan for viruses on my own with
I have a very very bad trojan that will not allow my graphics to work and I need a fix very fast.

you're making very little sense.  You need to take a few minutes and collect your thoughts.  Then summarize exactly what your issue is on exactly ONE line.  If you have logs or errors that you want to share include them in a pastebin
where are you getting this error exactly?
it happens with every video I try
if what others say is correct and this is a php error, then it's a server-side issue...
of course not, you aren't the server
you need to answer my question before we can help you.
you said all videos.  Surely that includes one that's not porn.
stop.  If you can't provide a sfw example, then we can't help you.
this channel is only for ubuntu support.  Move on.
